{"tid":1103041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"孫興慜：希望五六十年後 球迷依然不會忘記我","createTime":"2019-04-12T06:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T08:21:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfba22a08e7296442b3ee6ed64bf0cd10147788","tid":1103041,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"孫興慜接受採訪<br />\n<br />\n對曼城的比賽後孫興慜表示：「這是我的夢想，我一直都認為，你如果樂觀地思考，就會有樂觀的事情發生。」<br />\n<br />\n 「我相信隊友、球迷和新球場，我們的表現真是不可思議。」<br />\n<br />\n  在新球場連續入球後，孫興慜的名字將載入熱刺史冊。他表示：「我希望五六十年後人們不會忘記我。在這裡踢球，入球，並贏下這樣的比賽讓我感覺非常榮幸。我在熱刺學到了很多，感謝你們給我這樣的機會。」"},{"pid":"6a0a2a25522437001ba9a83d27283bd7576d1d33","tid":1103041,"uid":19126,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"反正獎杯櫃大把位，擺埋你張車頭相入去完全冇問題啦"},{"pid":"38d5a28cb495ea9507ad9704af272fd23656f633","tid":1103041,"uid":8968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"點X得呀!"},{"pid":"ea25b0c547c6e7a4c4327173eedc8cc745bf44a4","tid":1103041,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0a2a25522437001ba9a83d27283bd7576d1d33","tid":1103041,"uid":19126,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"反正獎杯櫃大把位，擺埋你張車頭相入去完全冇問題啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爛口到⋯"},{"pid":"0c8829aae78a6b706949f6748c1fb14df2578987","tid":1103041,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea25b0c547c6e7a4c4327173eedc8cc745bf44a4","tid":1103041,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0a2a25522437001ba9a83d27283bd7576d1d33","tid":1103041,"uid":19126,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"反正獎杯櫃大把位，擺埋你張車頭相入去完全冇問題啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爛口到⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:5